\f0\b0 Common asthma triggers: dust mites, pet hair, pollen,\
exercise, cold air, cigarette smoke. Allergy triggers depend on the person (foods, mold,\
insect stings). Avoiding known triggers (like keeping pets out of bedrooms, using\
allergy-proof covers on pillows) helps reduce attacks.\

